name: Wizard Pixel Willy Wonka
description: Arthur Slugworth had made progress in the "everlasting gobstopper" research. At least it looked that way.  There were people who wanted to help him. He took a lot of people behind him. They thought he was strong and took shelter in him.  But they were wrong.  Because Arthur Slugworth was attached to Willy Wonka from the very beginning.
